      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa) and yield strength (880 MPa) for Ti-6Al-4V sourced from batch-specific mill test reports. UHMWPE block properties from literature (ASTM F648). Screw and rod geometry inputs derived from CMM measurements of production components. Cortical fixation depth measured per F1717 protocol. Screening sensitivity analysis identified elastic modulus and fixation depth as primary input drivers; nominal values confirmed appropriate for the test population."
    },
